01:08:46,293 --> 01:08:47,748
agent. She'll take it from there.

1020
01:08:47,874 --> 01:08:49,958
She's the one who is going to
get you into the premiere.

1021
01:08:50,043 --> 01:08:51,568
It'll be you, her, and two

1022
01:08:51,569 --> 01:08:53,796
German-born members
