arrangements you're going to need.

1024
01:08:58,092 --> 01:08:59,301
How will I know her?

1025
01:08:59,385 --> 01:09:02,638
I suspect that won't be
too much trouble for you.

1026
01:09:03,723 --> 01:09:06,490
Your contact is Bridget
von Hammersmark.

1027
01:09:06,491 --> 01:09:08,227
Bridget von Hammersmark?

1028
01:09:09,395 --> 01:09:12,481
The German movie star
is working for England?

1029
01:09:12,565 --> 01:09:15,150
Yes, for the last two years now.

1030
01:09:15,235 --> 01:09:18,737
One could even say that Operation
Kino was her brainchild.

1031
01:09:18,863 --> 01:09:21,156
- Indeed.
- Got the gist?

1032
01:09:21,241 --> 01:09:23,909
I think so, sir. Paris
when it sizzles.

1033
01:09:25,203 --> 01:09:27,996
The village of Nadine

1034
01:09:28,081 --> 01:09:29,504
You didn't say the goddamn

1035
01:09:29,505 --> 01:09:31,583
rendezvous is in a
fucking basement.

1036
01:09:31,709 --> 01:09:34,503
- I didn't know.
- You said it was in a tavern.

1037
01:09:34,587 --> 01:09:37,256
- It is a tavern.
- Yeah, in a basement.

1038
01:09:37,924 --> 01:09:40,759
You know, fighting in a basement
offers a lot of difficulties.

1039
01:09:40,885 --> 01:09:44,179
Number one being, you're
fighting in a basement.

1040
01:09:44,264 --> 01:09:46,098
What if we go in there and
she's not even there?

1041
01:09:46,224 --> 01:09:47,432
We wait.

1042
01:09:48,268 --> 01:09:52,354
Don't worry. She's a British
spy. She'll make the rendezvous.

