1044
01:10:18,631 --> 01:10:21,133
I hear you're pretty
good with that.

1045
01:10:24,929 --> 01:10:27,973
You know, we're not looking
for trouble right now.

1046
01:10:28,308 --> 01:10:31,810
Simply making contact with our
agent. Should be uneventful.

1047
01:10:33,646 --> 01:10:38,483
However, the off chance I'm
wrong, things prove eventful,

1048
01:10:39,777 --> 01:10:42,654
I need to know we can
all remain calm.

1049
01:10:47,327 --> 01:10:48,827
I don't look calm to you?

1050
01:10:51,748 --> 01:10:56,668
Well, now that you put it
like that, I guess you do.

1051
01:11:11,809 --> 01:11:14,545
This Jerry of yours, Stiglitz, not

1052
01:11:14,546 --> 01:11:17,522
exactly the loquacious
type, is he?

1053
01:11:19,359 --> 01:11:23,111
Is that the kind of man you
need? Loquacious type?

1054
01:11:24,864 --> 01:11:27,366
Fair point, Lieutenant.

1055
01:11:29,702 --> 01:11:32,454
So you all get in trouble in
there, what are we supposed to do?

1056
01:11:32,538 --> 01:11:34,706
Make bets on how it all comes out?

1057
01:11:35,959 --> 01:11:39,127
If we get into trouble,
we can handle it.

1058
01:11:40,672 --> 01:11:43,548
But if trouble does happen,
we need you to make damn sure

1059
01:11:43,675 --> 01:11:47,803
no Germans, or French, for that
matter, escape from that basement.

1060
01:11:48,721 --> 01:11:52,975
If Frau von Hammersmark's cover is
compromised, the mission is kaput.

1061
01:11:53,351 --> 01:11:56,084
Speaking of Frau von
Hammersmark, whose

1062
01:11:56,085 --> 01:11:59,022
idea was it for the
death-trap rendezvous?

1063
01:11:59,983 --> 01:12:03,151
- She chose the spot.
- Isn't that just dandy?

1064
01:12:03,236 --> 01:12:07,155
Look, she's not a military
strategist. She's just an actress.

1065
01:12:07,573 --> 01:12:09,424
You don't got to be
Stonewall Jackson to

1066
01:12:09,425 --> 01:12:11,410
know you don't want to
fight in a basement.

1067
01:12:11,494 --> 01:12:13,495
She wasn't picking
a place to fight.

1068
01:12:13,579 --> 01:12:16,415
She was picking a place
isolated and without Germans.

1069
01:12:16,833 --> 01:12:18,000
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1070
01:12:18,084 --> 01:12:19,251
So, I'm male...

1071
01:12:19,419 --> 01:12:21,586
I'm a fictional, literary
character from the past...

1072
01:12:21,838 --> 01:12:24,589
