01:13:02,545 --> 01:13:03,745
Is my blood brother
Old Shatterhand?

1093
01:13:03,746 --> 01:13:04,746
Yes.

1094
01:13:04,797 --> 01:13:05,881
Did Karl May write me?

1095
01:13:05,965 --> 01:13:07,049
Yes.

1096
01:13:07,133 --> 01:13:08,216
So who are you?

1097
01:13:08,468 --> 01:13:11,053
I am "Winnetou," chief
of the Apaches.

1098
01:13:11,471 --> 01:13:12,596
Yes.

1099
01:13:13,264 --> 01:13:14,723
That was good. That was
good. That was good.

1100
01:13:14,932 --> 01:13:16,308
Now down with the glasses.

1101
01:13:16,726 --> 01:13:19,478
Cheers.

1102
01:13:26,319 --> 01:13:27,486
(FEMALE SERGEANT SPEAKING GERMAN)

1103
01:13:27,612 --> 01:13:28,653
Attention.

1104
01:13:34,118 --> 01:13:35,160
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1105
01:13:35,244 --> 01:13:36,328
Hello, my lovelies.

1106
01:13:36,829 --> 01:13:37,954
Take a seat.

1107
01:13:38,915 --> 01:13:40,863
I will join you in
moments. I'm just saying

1108
01:13:40,864 --> 01:13:42,501
goodbye to my five
new friends here.

1109
01:13:43,503 --> 01:13:45,796
No hurry, Frau von
Hammersmark. Take your time.

1110
01:13:46,172 --> 01:13:47,839
Enjoy yourself. We'll be
just over here waiting.

1111
01:13:54,680 --> 01:13:55,847
(SPEAKING FRENCH AND GERMAN)

1112
01:13:55,932 --> 01:13:58,517
Eric, my love. Those are the
friends I've been waiting for.

1113
01:13:58,684 --> 01:14:00,352
Please treat them to
anything they like.

1114
01:14:00,436 --> 01:14:01,436
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1115
01:14:01,521 --> 01:14:03,355
Frau von Hammersmark.
Your wish is my command.

1116
01:14:04,982 --> 01:14:06,024
Officers...

1117
01:14:06,359 --> 01:14:07,993
it would appear the drinks
are on the Fräulein.

1118
01:14:09,028 --> 01:14:10,779
- What would you like?
- Whiskey.

1119
01:14:10,863 --> 01:14:11,947
Two whiskeys.

1120
01:14:12,365 --> 01:14:14,324
- Three whiskeys.
- Three whiskeys, very well.

1121
01:14:15,868 --> 01:14:17,035
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1122
01:14:17,120 --> 01:14:18,370
I wish you a wonderful evening.

1123
01:14:18,496 --> 01:14:20,372
- Same to you.
- I thank you.

1124
01:14:20,623 --> 01:14:22,332
Your card.

1125
01:14:22,667 --> 01:14:23,708
Yes, you're right.

1126
01:14:24,961 --> 01:14:26,044
Let's see.

1127
01:14:27,380 --> 01:14:30,048
Genghis Khan. I would
never have gotten that.

1128
01:14:30,299 --> 01:14:31,466
But of course you would have.

1129
01:14:31,717 --> 01:14:32,717
Hello, darling.

1130
01:14:35,138 --> 01:14:36,179
How are you?

1131
01:14:38,975 --> 01:14:40,392
So good to see you.

1132
01:14:49,235 --> 01:14:50,235
(SPEAKING GERMAN SOFTLY)

1133
01:14:50,361 --> 01:14:52,904
I thought this place was supposed
to have more French than Germans?

1134
01:14:54,157 --> 01:14:56,158
Yes, normally that's true.

1135
01:14:56,325 --> 01:14:59,578
The Sergeant over there's
wife just had a baby.

1136
01:15:00,246 --> 01:15:02,898
And his commanding
officer gave him and

1137
01:15:02,899 --> 01:15:05,417
