off to celebrate.

1138
01:15:07,420 --> 01:15:08,420
We should leave.

1139
01:15:09,088 --> 01:15:10,172
No.

1140
01:15:10,756 --> 01:15:11,840
We should stay.

1141
01:15:12,091 --> 01:15:13,425
For one drink at least.

1142
01:15:14,260 --> 01:15:15,510
I've been waiting
for you in a bar.

1143
01:15:16,762 --> 01:15:19,014
It would look strange if we
left before we had a drink.

1144
01:15:19,348 --> 01:15:22,267
She's right. Just be calm
and enjoy your whiskey.

1145
01:15:25,438 --> 01:15:27,105
(SPEAKING FRENCH)

1146
01:15:28,274 --> 01:15:29,441
Mathilda...

1147
01:15:29,525 --> 01:15:30,609
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1148
01:15:30,693 --> 01:15:32,627
come join us in the game. Take
Frau Hammersmark's place.

1149
01:15:33,112 --> 01:15:34,946
(SPEAKING FRENCH)

1150
01:15:40,077 --> 01:15:41,203
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1151
01:15:41,287 --> 01:15:42,704
She would love to play the game.

1152
01:15:44,916 --> 01:15:47,292
I will translate... and protect.

1153
01:15:47,627 --> 01:15:48,727
Don't worry, pretty little thing.

1154
01:15:48,794 --> 01:15:53,131
If any of these wolves gets out
of line, I'll kick their ass in.

1155
01:15:53,382 --> 01:15:54,424
Watch.

1156
01:15:56,802 --> 01:15:57,886
Rip off his nose.

1157
01:16:05,561 --> 01:16:06,561
Stop it.

1158
01:16:06,646 --> 01:16:08,980
Schnapps, schnapps, take your
